{"tid":540062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[紅色恐怖] 浸會大學多名學生接獲通知出席紀律聆訊","createTime":"2018-01-25T06:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T10:22:43.000Z","uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26c4da6f4dc562fbe461a3cf8447c1cf30f94a69","tid":540062,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"兩名浸會大學學生因為在校內抗議時涉嫌威脅教師被暫時停學，包括學生會會長劉子頎及中醫系學生陳樂行。浸大學生會編輯委員會在社交網頁表示，中午時陸續有參與抗議行動的學生收到校方電郵，要求出席紀律聆訊，涉及的學生包括編委會總編輯何浩賢、教務議會學生代表廖偉濂等。<br />\n<br />\n劉子頎及陳樂行，早上分別出席電台節目，劉子頎說同意就抗議時態度欠佳受罰，願意就態度問題致歉，但不認同實際上有造成人身威脅，對被停學感到震驚，認為未經紀律聆訊就停課是未審先判，不合往常程序。他又指，聯絡過計劃就事件發起罷課的同學，他們的行動會改為明日會在校內集會遊行，爭取撤回停課決定。另外，浸大偉衡體育中心及鄰近的屋苑外牆，上午被發現噴有「不要普通話」、「歧視」等字句，警員到場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=989165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D989165&d=0o5azslwCYS4FXC%2BZHkPgjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7bbcb6e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=989165</a>"},{"pid":"150ca52fc08f334b011b83f63a16af34a6b48916","tid":540062,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec2aaca4522113acbe7048f85c2aefb4a6d197f","tid":540062,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"唔審停學=白色恐怖<br />\n唔停學審你=紅色恐怖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95962ace6e7833d77e1d68658512e91896165515","tid":540062,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7125115d098a82f9928dfdbe7ef41b85cf78bfa6","tid":540062,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:14:36.000Z","msg":"人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3186ee788d0f239e55e98bf1c5524a8ccebd5ab6","tid":540062,"uid":82587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:20:45.000Z","msg":"全校一齊講粗口運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc59dbff52a6fb311402941d8bdbba6bb3129c6","tid":540062,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3186ee788d0f239e55e98bf1c5524a8ccebd5ab6","tid":540062,"uid":82587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:20:45.000Z","msg":"全校一齊講粗口運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:22:43.000Z","msg":"之後全校教職員打冷震，好暴力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}